comments: Markkanen (CHI) establishes legal position in Bullock's (CHI) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Young (CHI) and Robinson (NYK) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Randle (NYK) hands off the ball and is firming up in Williams' (CHI) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Robinson (NYK) contests LaVine's (CHI) dunk at the basket and any contact that occurs is marginal.
Robinson's (NYK) inbound pass is thrown into the outside of the boundary line before being touched in bounds and is therefore never thrown directly in bounds.
Williams (CHI) places his arm to Barrett's (NYK) front and marginal contact occurs during his drive.
Markkanen (CHI) jumps alongside of Barrett's (NYK) path to the basket and absorbs any body contact during his driving shot attempt.
White (CHI) briefly places his arm against Robinson (NYK) and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the loose ball.
Robinson (NYK) places his hand against Young's (CHI) side but Young loses control of the ball on his own and the contact is marginal.
Young (CHI) cleanly deflects the pass to Barrett (NYK) before incidental contact occurs.
Barrett (NYK) briefly grasps Young's (CHI) arm and disengages as he gathers the loose ball.
LaVine (CHI) makes contact to Bullock's (NYK) arm and contact affects his SQBR.
Temple (CHI) briefly places an arm near Barrett's (NYK) side as he deflects the pass attempt and marginal contact occurs.
Randle (NYK) briefly places an arm against Young's (CHI) front and marginal contact occurs during his shot attempt near the rim.
LaVine (CHI) commits a take foul on Quickley (NYK).
